data.description:
**Price Reduced**

This 2,716 sq. ft. home offers nearly a 180 degree view of Nueces Bay, making it the perfect place to relax and enjoy the beautiful scenery. The home features 4 bedrooms, all with water views, two bedroom suites, and one downstairs bedroom has a private bath entrance. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops and is perfect for cooking and entertaining guests. The spacious living area has great views, a fireplace, and a vaulted ceiling.

In addition there is also a spacious sunroom with a super quiet mini split AC so you can enjoy the relaxing views year round. There is also a deck across the back with a covered patio. The in ground pool is on a terrace so you get that infinity feel when you are in the pool.

The home also has a 50 year metal roof, water softener system, and easy and beautiful drive to Corpus Christi.

This home is truly a paradise and is perfect for anyone looking for a home with stunning views.
